1
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:58,680
Your Majesty.

2
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,960
The envoy of Northern Di requests an urgent audience.

3
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:03,290
He says it is a matter of great importance.

4
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:07,720
Granted.

5
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:12,560
The envoy of Northern Di pays respects to His Majesty, the Emperor of Great Feng.

6
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,320
You may rise.

7
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:17,080
I take the liberty of requesting an audience with Your Majesty.

8
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,200
It is truly a matter of grave importance.

9
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:22,080
Please dismiss your attendants.

10
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,479
Speak.

11
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,090
You were in such a hurry to see me

12
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:45,880
just for a landscape painting?

13
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:49,009
Please examine this painting carefully, Your Majesty.

14
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,000
Yan Qingshu.

15
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:55,920
Xiao Jingyan.

16
00:01:56,520 --> 00:02:00,120
This painting is known as the map of the Heishui Valley iron mine.

17
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,240
Just based on this painting,

18
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:04,040
you call this a secret map of an ore vein?

19
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,240
Whether it is true or false,

20
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:08,800
Your Majesty will know once you send someone to investigate.

21
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,880
This gift comes at the perfect time.

22
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,480
Northern Di is indeed my good ally.

23
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,079
The Khan entrusted me to say,

24
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:25,320
since the Emperor of Great Feng gave us ten cities,

25
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,440
it is only proper to reciprocate.

26
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,320
Heaven helps me.

27
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,079
I was just worrying about having no excuse to punish him,

28
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,480
and now I have this ironclad proof of treason.

29
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,120
Guards.

30
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,920
Imprison Xiao Jingyan immediately.

31
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,200
He will be charged with treason.

32
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,560
He will be executed on a chosen day.

33
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,320
Summon Yan Qingshu to the palace to see me immediately.

34
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,520
Yes, Your Majesty.

35
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,900
Yes, Your Majesty.

36
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,440
Lord Xiao.

37
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,480
I am ordered by His Majesty

38
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:14,720
to escort you to the imperial prison for interrogation.

39
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:17,040
If you surrender,

40
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,920
your family will be spared.

41
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,520
My lord.

42
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,600
The Xiao Army is always on standby.

43
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:24,120
We will never let you fall into anyone else's hands.

44
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,640
Mo Yu.

45
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,360
I am here.

46
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:28,480
From now on,

47
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,680
everyone in the Xiao Army

48
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,090
is at the Princess's disposal.

49
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:33,960
Yes.

50
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,300
Protect yourself.

51
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,820
Wait for my return.

52
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,080
Wait.

53
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,320
Heir Xiao,

54
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,200
I trust you've been well.

55
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,040
Pardon my offense again.

56
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,640
Then I will trouble you, Commander Qin.

57
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,279
The Heir...

58
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,339
He just left like that?

59
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:34,040
Summon Yan Qingshu to the palace for an audience immediately.

60
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,680
Mo Yu,

61
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,680
deliver this letter quickly.

62
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,520
Understood.

63
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,080
Princess, please be careful.

64
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:42,010
The Xiao Army is always on standby.

65
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,200
Yan Qingshu, take a good look.

66
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,000
This is the evidence of you and Xiao Jingyan

67
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,400
colluding with Beidi.

68
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,520
What else do you have to say?

69
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,200
We did not draw this map.

70
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,560
This attempt to frame us is too clumsy.

71
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,820
The evidence is solid.

72
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,240
How dare you argue?

73
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,440
My signature

74
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:11,200
and Prince Xiao's red private seal are fake.

75
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,400
Are you saying

76
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,400
that I am framing you two?

77
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:19,280
The map of Heishui Valley that I drew,

78
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:22,280
I personally gave to the Right Worthy Prince of Beidi.

79
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:25,220
How did it end up in Your Majesty's hands?

80
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,960
Could it be

81
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,760
that the Right Worthy Prince gave my map

82
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,920
to Your Majesty?

83
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:33,080
Yan Qingshu, Yan Qingshu.

84
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,240
How dare you bite back

85
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,540
and slander me?

86
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,770
I wouldn't dare.

87
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:49,040
I just looked at the drawing carefully again.

88
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:52,640
It indeed looks like the one I gave to Prince Youxian.

89
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,440
However, I am confused

90
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,260
why this drawing is in Your Majesty's hands.

91
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,840
Please enlighten me, Your Majesty.

92
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:01,960
Yan Qingshu,

93
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:05,320
don't even think about getting what you want from me.

94
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:08,000
Hand over the Records of Officials immediately.

95
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,680
Otherwise,

96
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,760
I will make the eight hundred soldiers of the Xiao Army

97
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,360
be buried with Xiao Jingyan.

98
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,800
Fine, play dead.

99
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,440
Guards!

100
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,880
Summon the royal physician.

101
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,600
Your Majesty.

102
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,240
Lady Yan's pulse is erratic.

103
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,360
She seems to have been poisoned by a rare toxin and her vitality is dissipating.

104
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:42,020
I am afraid she only has a few months left to live.

105
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,920
Yan Qingshu, listen to me.

106
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,600
Hand over the records of the officials,

107
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,659
and I will spare Xiao Jingyan's life.

108
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,800
Otherwise, I will immediately order

109
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,540
him to be executed by a thousand cuts.

110
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,120
I am a dying person.

111
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,680
I can't even save my own life,

112
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,690
so how can I care about the lives of others?

113
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,480
Kill me or torture me,

114
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,920
do as you please.

115
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,080
Good.

116
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,280
Good.

117
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,600
Guards,

118
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,740
take her away and guard her strictly.

119
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:31,280
Use every means possible to keep her alive.

120
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,600
I will not allow her to die.

121
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,840
Yes, Your Majesty.

122
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,320
The game has reached its end.

123
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,400
The real contest

124
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,600
starts now.

125
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,240
I am the Son of Heaven.

126
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,360
My will

127
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,680
is the will of Heaven.

128
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,360
My choice

129
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,840
is the law.

130
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,960
No one can judge me.

131
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:11,960
No one.

132
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:20,840
No one can judge me.

133
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,920
I, Yan Qingshu, pay my respects to Your Majesty.

134
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,440
Yan Qingshu.

135
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:53,320
It's been a few days. Have you thought it through?

136
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,800
Exchanging the officials' records for Xiao Jingyan

137
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,200
and the lives of the 800 Xiao family troops.

138
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,370
My patience is limited.

139
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,120
Your Majesty need not repeat yourself.

140
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:06,160
I only have a few days left to live

141
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:09,320
and have no more attachments to this world.

142
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:12,600
Now, I only act for my own peace of mind.

143
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,280
Your Majesty's relentless pressure

144
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,560
annoys me.

145
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:21,160
Why not speak your mind to me?

146
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,800
If I am at ease,

147
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,800
perhaps

148
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,960
I might remember something.

149
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,960
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

150
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,200
My days are numbered.

151
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:31,240
Your Majesty's words

152
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:34,520
will be buried with me.

153
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,130
Alright.

154
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:39,120
I will speak my mind to you today.

155
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:43,330
The Duke and the Marquis of Zhenbei

156
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,220
were pillars of the state.

157
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,480
It's a pity

158
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,740
they were ignorant of the times and inflexible,

159
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,440
which ultimately brought disaster upon them.

160
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:56,640
By the times and flexibility, Your Majesty means

161
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,000
Your Majesty

162
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:02,880
conspiring to illegally forge weapons

163
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:05,160
and selling them to the Northern Di?

164
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,000
Insolent!

165
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,680
Even if I did it,

166
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:09,760
so what?

167
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:12,280
The borders have been at war for years.

168
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,540
The treasury is empty.

169
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,720
Without money and grain, how can we support the army?

170
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,780
Trading with the Northern Di was a matter of expediency

171
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,370
to solve an urgent problem.

172
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,520
Even if I did it,

173
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,320
it was all for the country.

174
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,250
What a way to be all for the country.

175
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,240
Then,

176
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,720
ceding the northern borders and Tong Pass,

177
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:34,880
dozens of military strongholds, to the Northern Di

178
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,160
was also Your Majesty's expedient measure

179
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:39,360
to enrich the treasury?

180
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,000
That was to end the war.

181
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,770
You are just a woman.

182
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,020
How could you know the cruelty of war?

183
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,560
I couldn't bear to see the people displaced

184
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,490
and the land engulfed in war again.

185
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,120
Exchanging a few cities for a century of peace,

186
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,450
what's wrong with that?

187
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,280
Should we end up like the neighboring country,

188
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,880
trampled by the iron hooves of the Northern Di,

189
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:02,140
with corpses littering the fields, to be considered wise?

190
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,280
What noble intentions.

191
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,640
Then,

192
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:12,960
colluding with the Khan of Beidi,

193
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:16,400
having shadow guards disguise as Beidi imperial guards,

194
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:20,240
and hunting down the Heir of Zhenbei who investigated the weapons case...

195
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,240
For what reason?

196
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,880
Was that also for peace?

197
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,600
Also for the people?

198
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,890
I could not let anyone else know

199
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,800
the truth behind those inferior weapons.

200
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,200
It was you, Your Majesty.

201
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,080
Three years ago,

202
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,640
the weapons that caused the tragic defeat of the Zhenbei Army

203
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:40,680
and the wrongful deaths of the Marquis of Zhenbei and 3,000 soldiers,

204
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:43,960
were ordered by you through Prince Ling.

205
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,140
Why would you ruin your own defenses?

206
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,360
Only by letting the Late Emperor see his flawed decisions

207
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:51,620
could I implement my national policies.

208
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:54,140
I did this all for the grand vision of Dafeng.

209
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,000
How could ordinary people like you understand?

210
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,640
What a grand vision.

211
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,160
For your grand vision,

212
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,720
you poisoned the Late Emperor?

213
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,480
Shut up!

214
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:07,880
He forced me.

215
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,290
He never cared about me.

216
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,080
Only that reckless Crown Prince...

217
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,120
A few days ago,

218
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:19,480
what Yan Qingshu said in his letter,

219
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,000
I

220
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:25,080
could hardly believe it.

221
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:27,800
Now,

222
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,680
hearing it with my own ears,

223
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:32,680
I am truly

224
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,680
burning with grief.

225
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:40,160
Poisoning the late Emperor,

226
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,120
violating human relations,

227
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:44,800
it's intolerable to heaven.

228
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,620
I am the mandate of heaven.

229
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:49,560
Everything I did was for the Dafeng Empire.

230
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:52,080
The process is not important.

231
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,810
The result trumps everything.

232
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,200
I have not let my ancestors down.

233
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,200
Dafeng is still here, and the people are safe.

234
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,120
That is enough.

235
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:03,080
Colluding with the enemy and betraying the country,

236
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:05,360
ceding territory to survive,

237
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,080
and even

238
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:11,040
killing the father to usurp the throne.

239
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,720
A foolish ruler,

240
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:16,080
a wicked ruler.

241
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:21,320
How can we let him continue to

242
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,640
taint the throne

243
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:27,080
and mess up the court?

244
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:28,480
Yes.

245
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,280
The laws are archaic.

246
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,560
The current laws

247
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:34,160
are not worthy of judging my merits and faults.

248
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,570
I want to amend the laws.

249
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:39,010
I will tell future generations

250
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:40,160
that everything I have done

251
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,560
was to protect the state.

252
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:43,760
I am not wrong.

253
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,720
Your Majesty is wrong.

254
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,360
Why are you here?

255
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:00,720
Your Majesty,

256
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,760
we old ministers

257
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:06,040
heard everything.

258
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,840
Poisoning the late Emperor,

259
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,880
framing loyal subjects,

260
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:12,840
colluding with the enemy,

261
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:15,240
ceding territory for peace,

262
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:18,760
hunting down the descendants of the loyal.

263
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:21,920
Now you even want to tamper with the law

264
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,080
to cover up your wrongdoings.

265
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,120
Your Majesty,

266
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:31,000
your sins are so grave

267
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:33,920
that both man and God are outraged.

268
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:39,400
Your Majesty,

269
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:43,360
you have lost your virtue before the world.

270
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:47,280
I have no face to see our ancestors.

271
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:51,400
We, your loyal subjects, tearfully beg you,

272
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,400
for the sake of the state,

273
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,960
and the people,

274
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,920
Your Majesty,

275
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,920
to abdicate.

276
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:29,760
Cuimei

277
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,360
Cuimei

278
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,200
Yong

279
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,800
Weikun Huachao

280
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,820
Weikun Huachao

281
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:38,200
Longcong Biaohao

282
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:41,040
